{
  "stem": "13096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because we were taken for granted-- like we were inferior-- that we have to do all these thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because all our-- or-- our dignity was gone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We told, there's bromo in our-- in our food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And besides all these things, also all the woman, they never had the-- the-- their periods.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because otherwise, how can you have in there, you know, all these millions of people?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that is to stop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And many of them, you know, after the war, they never had any children, on account we know they had too many months eating of this bromo.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were ruined for lives.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many people today, in Israel-- but they-- thank God, in our group, nothing happened-- only a couple that didn't have children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we only stay in captivity about 10 months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But other people that are still-- like from Poland, from Holland, they were before us taken by the Germans, they were just, you know, for life like that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyhow, I was saying, we arrive in those blocks without food, because the time for the food was already-- distribution of the food was gone.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it were we have to wait for the following day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next morning, when they took us to the-- to the out, you know, in the air, at 4 o'clock, usually every night-- it was when you arrive at the blocks.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was 3 o'clock, 1/2 past 3:00 at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were just trying to accommodate in the floor, whatever, to find a little sleep after, you know, so-- such a long day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "4 o'clock, they start, you know, screaming-- out, out, out, in German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN]!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It means, that's the time has come to be-- you know, the-- the-- the time to call you, you know, for the counting.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
